quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  26,34,"Fir’auni\tavuga\tabwira\tabakuru\tbamukikuje\tati :-\tmu\tvy’ukuri\tuyu n’umurozi afise ubumenyi buhanitse"
  26,35,"Agomba\tabakure\tmugihugu\tcanyu\takoresheje\tuburozi\tbwiwe,\tnone mwebwe mubivuga ko iki"
  26,36,"Nabo\tbavuga\tbati:-\tnimumuhe\tumwanya\thamwe\tna\tmwene\twabo hanyuma mubarungike mugisagara caho bakoraniriza abantu bose"
  26,37,Bazokuzanira ibihangange vy’abarozi bose bafise ubumenyi buhanitse
  26,38,"Barakoranijwe\tabarozi\tbose,\tmumwanya\tn’umusi\twagenewe\turwo rubanza"
  26,39,"Baca babwirwa abantu bati :- none mwese mwamaze gukorana"
  26,40,Nkumbure tuzobakurikira abo barozi niba aribo bazoronka intsinzi
  26,41,"Rero mugihe bashika abo barozi baciye babwira Fir’auni bati:- mbega turaronka impembo nitwa tahukana intsinzi"
  26,42,"Fir’auni abishura ati:- egome kandi mwebwe muzoba muri bamwe mu bantu banje bizigirwa"
  26,43,"Intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) ibabwira babarozi iti:- nimujugunye ivyo mushobora kujugunya"
  26,44,"Bajugunya imigozi yabo hamwe n’inkoni zabo nukuvuga bati:- kububasha bwa Fir’auni ni twebwe bene intsinzi"
  26,45,Hanyuma intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) ica ijugunya inkoni yayo hasi yankoni ica iramiragura ivyo abo barozi badukanye
  26,46,Aho niho babarozi bose barwa hasi barapfukama
  26,47,"Baca bavuga bati:- turemeye Umuremyi w’abantu bose"
  26,48,Umuremyi wa Mussa (iii) hamwe na Haruna (iii)
  26,49,"Fir’auni avuga ati:- mbega mwamwemeye uyo Mussa (iii) imbere yuko ndabaha uruhusha? Ntankeka niwe yabaye umukuru wanyu yabigishije uburozi, ubu rero muzotahura neza, ubu ngiye gucagagura amaboko n’amaguru yanyu ndabitandukanije hanyuma nce ndababamba kubiti mwese"
  26,50,"Nabo baca bavuga bati:- ntaco bitwaye mu vy’ukuri twese tuzo subira ku Muremyi wacu"
  26,51,"Ntankeka twebwe twizeye yuko Umuremyi wacu azotugirira ikigongwe kubera ibicumuro vyacu, kuko twebwe tubaye abambere mukwemera kuba aba Isilamu b’ukuri"
  26,52,"Twara\tmurungikiye\tintumwa\ty’Imana\tMussa\t(iii)\tubutumire\tyuko yogenda ku bantu banje mugihe c’ijoro ntankeka muzo kurikiranwa"